<title>UK: London gold fixes firmer at $342.40, quiet.</title>
<headline>London gold fixes firmer at $342.40, quiet.</headline>
<text>
<p>GOLD - Fixed at $342.40 vs $341.10 previously. Very quiet due to Ascension Day holiday in most of Europe. Some support buying against weaker dollar. May try higher in New York.</p>
<p>SILVER - Quiet and rangebound. $4.75/$4.77, up three cents.</p>
<p>PLATINUM - Firmer by $3.50 at $375.25/$376.25.</p>
<p>PALLADIUM - Up $1.50 at $156.50/$157.50.</p>
